description:
And finally a new Inspector Canardo - Inspector Canardo 12 - Innocent.
And this one is for once translated by DarthScanner, editorial work and major proofreading by me, and retexted by Fenrir.

A nanny from the prestigious Bellegarden Institute, has been charged with murdering the couple she worked for, the Montaldos. The Institute hires Inspector Canardo to prove their former student innocent, and he heads to the US to get to work on the case.
But did the girl really kill her employers? Her description of the events clash with the explanation of the only person other person in the house, apart from the Montaldos son, Johnny, who's in a mental hospital after witnessing the murder.
So Canardo will have a hard time proving the pretty young nanny...innocent!
